item.title: SoftLayer_Product_Package_Item_Category_Group
item.description: SoftLayer_Product_Package_Item_Category_Group Datatype Description This class is used to organize categories for a service offering. A service offering (usually) contains multiple categories (e.g., server, os, disk0, ram). This class allows us to organize the prices into related item category groups. Local itemCategoryId The item category id associated with this group. Type: integer packageId The service offering id associated with this group. Type: integer
